---
import DocsPageShell from '../../components/DocsPageShell.astro'
import PromptCard from '../../components/PromptCard.astro'
---

<DocsPageShell
  title="Skills And Prompts"
  description="Use prompts for straightforward live questions. Use skills when you want your agent to follow a repeatable operator flow."
  eyebrow="Operator Guide"
  canonical="https://ouroboros.bot/docs/skills-and-prompts/"
  intro="Simple questions can stop at a prompt. If the job has a repeatable sequence and common failure modes, point your agent at a skill instead."
>
  <PromptCard
    prompt="List the skills currently published for Ouroboros and tell me which one is most relevant to what I'm working on right now."
    footnote="Your agent checks the current skills manifest and recommends the right handoff."
  />

  <!-- Two-column comparison -->
  <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[10px] text-scale/60 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Prompt first when</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-mist leading-relaxed">
        <li>You need a current answer to a specific question.</li>
        <li>You want your agent to inspect the live source and summarize what it finds.</li>
        <li>The task is narrow enough that structure would only slow it down.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[10px] text-scale/60 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Use a skill when</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-mist leading-relaxed">
        <li>The task has a repeatable sequence and common failure modes.</li>
        <li>You want the agent to follow a known operator flow.</li>
        <li>You still want the agent to inspect the current code or environment before acting.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exit links -->
  <div class="pt-6 border-t border-canopy/15 space-y-3">
    <a href="/docs" class="group block text-sm text-mist/70 hover:text-bone transition-colors">
      See all the guides. <span class="text-scale/50 group-hover:text-scale transition-colors">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/build-ai-agent-from-scratch" class="group block text-sm text-mist/70 hover:text-bone transition-colors">
      Understand the primitive underneath. <span class="text-scale/50 group-hover:text-scale transition-colors">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</DocsPageShell>
